"7  ears yellow corn, shucked","4 cups unsalted chicken stock","1 tablespoon chopped fresh thyme","1 1/2 teaspoons kosher salt, divided","8 ounces Yukon Gold potatoes, cut into 3/4-in. pieces","1 cup half-and-half","1/4 cup unsalted butter, divided","1 teaspoon black pepper","1 pound medium shrimp, peeled and deveined","3 tablespoons chopped fresh chives, divided"